{"tid":994612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人女朋友仲好似未戒奶咁？？","createTime":"2019-01-24T23:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T13:29:16.000Z","uid":115361,"like":12,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1aaaaec3d46fecb6baba4eff5a9aba234ebf7461","tid":994612,"uid":115361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"一開始都仲係借啲意摸下我心口<br />\n依家搭親車都奉放隻手係我個心口掃粒lin <br />\n搞到我扶手都唔鬼捉淨係捉佢個對臭手<br />\n然後佢就會視姦我個心口<br />\n同我講「我見到佢（Lin)啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返到屋企更加痴撚線<br />\n以前衰多口<br />\n見到啲人妻餵BB飲奶 <br />\n就懶搞笑咁話「個BB渣ga  我細個都係飲自己啲奶 自給自足 唔使驚餓親」<br />\n之後我女朋友對眼就好似識發光咁<br />\n日日都喊哂口話自己要飲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係我有次做我激嬲佢<br />\n佢就提出要罰我佢先會原諒我<br />\n個懲罰就係佢要啜我粒Lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好撚後悔當時屈服咗係佢淫威之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從個次之後每次見都好似雞咁要俾佢啜幾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢軟硬兼施完全拒絕唔到<br />\n佢條脷成日伸出黎掃黎掃去都算啦<br />\n問題係佢有啲肉緊得濟發神經仲會咬落去<br />\n痛到扑街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇手足有呢個困擾？<br />\n點先可以令到佢戒奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b10c0bf39175da817884100ca8b657b21be8f8","tid":994612,"uid":29070,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:23:08.000Z","msg":"咁樣唔好咩？"},{"pid":"792fd3f9c022c9ec84dcfdac7aacc830320e1a19","tid":994612,"uid":53029,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:26:18.000Z","msg":"一巴車落去啦"},{"pid":"5701bec300637bf4ff09239ee57f87f549f13a16","tid":994612,"uid":40470,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:27:42.000Z","msg":"都好既!好在你地呢D毒男淨係識性幻想唔會危害到呢個社會,但係我就替你地老